                "p": [
                    {
                        "value": "ALBA collections at the Tamiment Library."
                    },
                    {
                        "value": "Two files of materials by and relating to Leonard Sloan Torgoff, including articles and research material about his death in Spain, can be found in the \u003cspan class=\"ead-extref\"\u003eRobert Steck Papers\u003c/span\u003e.",
                        "extref": [
